text: Abh or ABH may refer to: * Abh (trigraph) * Abererch railway station, Wales, station code * Assault occasioning actual bodily harm, an offence in English law * Alpha Airport, Queensland, Australia, IATA code * Aviation boatswain's mates, handling, US Navy occupational rating * Central Asian Arabic, ISO 639-3 code * A Barbadian's Head on the flag of pirate Bartholomew Roberts
title: ABH
